file: bmptk/README

Bare Metal Programming Tool Kit main directory

more information:
   - http://www.voti.nl/bmptk
   - ./docs/html/index.html (might require running Doxygen)

This directory contains :

   files
      - bmptk.h            : top-level header file for bmptk
      - Doxygen            : settings file for doucmentation creation
      - Makefile.template  : template for a bmptk project(s) makefile
      - Makefile.inc       : included by the project makefile
      - README             : this file

   subdirectories
      - targets            : basic chip and board specific stuff
      - graphics           : stuff for pixel-accessible graphics
      - examples           : example directories
      - tools              : tools (executables)

